    "sections": {
        "description": "<p>Usage:<br />\nWhen using the display-posts shortcode plugin with the <code>meta_key=\"custom_field_name\"</code> and <code>meta_value=\"current\"</code> to list all posts that have the ID of the current page as the value of the specified custom field, add the <code>meta_is_id=\"true\"</code> to convert &#8220;current&#8221; to the correct ID.</p>\n",
        "installation": "<p>Just drop the plugin in the plugins directory and activate.</p>\n"
    },
    "short_description": "Convert &quot;current&quot; as the current page ID when using the display posts shortcode to query custom fields.",
